data.description: Come see this spacious 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home on 3.18 acres with stocked pond! Fish on your own private pond which is home to Brim, Tilapia and Catfish! This home has 2238 total square foot which offers an abundant amount of space and is move in ready. Home has large kitchen with custom cabinetry and a center island. Owner's suite is massive with french doors leading to an on suite and walk in closet. Attached to the owner's suite is a room perfect for a nursery, office or an owner retreat! Home is equipped with removable accessibility ramp. Close proximity to local schools and located just blocks from the center of the town of Hilliard. Schedule your showing before it's gone! Motivated Seller!
